<div class="space-y-8">
    <div class="text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex p-4 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-full mb-4">
            <i data-lucide="sparkles" class="w-12 h-12 text-purple-400"></i>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-2">سحر تحسين الصور بالذكاء الاصطناعي</h4>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm max-w-md mx-auto">ارفع دقة الصور الضعيفة، قلل التشويش، وحسن الألوان بلمسة واحدة من الـ AI.</p>
    </div>

    <form action="/api/enhance-image" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="space-y-6">
        <div class="relative h-64 border-4 border-dashed border-slate-700 rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-slate-900/50 hover:bg-slate-900/80 hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-all group overflow-hidden">
            <input type="file" name="image" accept="image/*" required class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer z-10">
            
            <div class="text-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
                <i data-lucide="image-plus" class="w-16 h-16 text-slate-600 mb-4 group-hover:text-purple-400"></i>
                <p class="text-slate-400 font-bold">اسحب الصورة هنا أو اضغط للاختيار</p>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs mt-2">JPG, PNG, WEBP (حتى 5 ميجابايت)</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-500 text-white py-5 rounded-3xl font-black text-2xl flex items-center justify-center gap-4 transition-all shadow-2xl shadow-purple-500/30">
            <i data-lucide="wand-2" class="w-8 h-8"></i> معالجة الصورة الآن
        </button>
    </form>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700/50 text-center">
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">قبل المعالجة 📉</p>
            <div class="h-2 w-full bg-slate-800 rounded-full mt-2 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="h-full bg-slate-700 w-1/3"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-purple-500/5 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-purple-500/10 text-center">
            <p class="text-xs text-purple-400">بعد المعالجة بالـ AI 📈</p>
            <div class="h-2 w-full bg-slate-800 rounded-full mt-2 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="h-full bg-purple-500 w-full animate-pulse"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
